<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 18:08:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列当局为南部撤离人员预订了双重酒店，部分人被告知离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</link><description>政府将斯德洛特撤离人员在酒店的住宿期限延长至2月底，但酒店已经为基布兹马根撤离人员预订了一月底的住宿。一名仅提前两周通知就被告知离开的撤离者表示，“我们不知所措”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</guid></item><item><title>《辛贝特法》备忘录将使以色列安全机构能够监视记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</link><description>该法律授权情报机构在计算机、手机所有者不知情的情况下对其进行秘密搜查。虽然一些职业在备忘录中受到保护，但记者却不受保护。民权组织称备忘录“忽视了政治影响力的危险”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:16:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</guid></item><item><title>艾美奖与会者对以色列-加沙战争双方表示声援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</link><description>“佩戴具有象征意义的黄丝带不仅具有人类的力量，而且还可以上镜” ■ 演员和业界人士佩戴各种别针，包括黄丝带、鸽子，甚至国际法院的鳞片，以表达对以色列与哈马斯战争的看法</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家监管机构发现国防部多年来忽视患有创伤后应激障碍的残疾退伍军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</link><description>国家审计长发现，用于扩大康复部门的预算的很大一部分尚未得到利用，以色列国防军退伍军人不了解自己的权利，并受到官僚主义障碍和缺乏数字访问的困扰</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</guid></item><item><title>教育部因阿拉伯以色列东道主而撤回对犹太活动的资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</link><description>“代表异族通婚的女性不能代表犹太文化”，该部在谈到记者兼主持人露西·阿哈里什时表示，她的丈夫是犹太法乌达明星查希·哈勒维。主办“促进多元化、进步和自由犹太教”年度活动的以色列理事会要求该部撤回其决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 12:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日100天后，加沙边境社区的以色列居民再也无法抑制愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</link><description>“你抛弃了我们直至死亡，我们的世界在你的注视下化为尘土” ■ 饱受蹂躏的加沙边境基布兹的“愤怒”幸存者聚集在以色列议会外，要求政府辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:59:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列军队决定给出详细答复时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</link><description>在战争期间经常发生的爆炸房屋内有居住者的情况中，以色列国防军倾向于保持含糊不清以掩盖“附带损害”的严重程度</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特：伊朗利用以色列人拍摄安全官员的家，影响公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</link><description>《辛贝特》证实了《国土报》的调查，调查显示伊朗情报机构运营煽动以色列人相互对抗、甚至招募以色列人的团体和页面，并揭露了至少另外三人</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称袭击了以色列驻伊拉克“摩萨德总部”，为加沙战争中“其指挥官被杀”报仇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</link><description>在伊朗声称摧毁了位于埃尔比勒的“摩萨德间谍总部”后，美国和法国谴责这次袭击是对伊拉克半自治库尔德斯坦主权的“鲁莽”和“令人担忧的侵犯”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间，以色列的民主衰落并未停止。在很多方面，情况变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</link><description>更多的监控、更多的枪支、更少的言论自由：内塔尼亚胡的联盟在 10 月 7 日的袭击后停止了削弱司法机构的计划，但战争却让它在没有这些的情况下实现了许多目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</link><description>21 岁的尼赞·谢斯勒 (Nitzan Schessler) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，周一在加沙南部的战斗中身亡。 37 岁的诺姆·阿什拉姆 (Noam Ashram) 周二因 12 月在加沙中部的战斗中受伤而死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</guid></item><item><title>以色列延长紧急令，阻止被拘留的加沙人见律师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-emergency-order-preventing-detained-gazans-from-seeing-a-lawyer/0000018d-114c-d71c-ad9f-53ce280d0000</link><description>以色列议会还批准了延长紧急命令的一读，该命令允许极右翼国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔降低巴勒斯坦安全囚犯的条件</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 08:54:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-extends-emergency-order-preventing-detained-gazans-from-seeing-a-lawyer/0000018d-114c-d71c-ad9f-53ce280d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列购买了一个大规模在线影响力系统来对抗反犹太主义和哈马斯暴行的否认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</link><description>10 月 7 日后不久，国防、情报和民间机构意识到，他们正在输给据消息人士称哈马斯“运转良好的心理和信息战机器”的在线战斗。因此，尽管担心未来政治滥用，他们还是悄悄购买了数字工具来打击虚假信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-bought-mass-online-influence-system-to-counter-antisemitism-hamas-atrocity-denial/0000018d-0d31-db13-affd-7d3532830000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构返回加沙可能穿越埃及边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</link><description>埃及担心以色列对过境点的控制将剥夺开罗在加沙的关键影响力。将其移交给巴勒斯坦权力机构可能会减轻这些担忧并有助于恢复加沙地带的正常状态 - 但目前不太可能发生</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/rafah-border-crossing-may-also-be-the-route-for-the-palestinian-authoritys-return-to-gaza/0000018d-0f44-d71c-ad9f-4fc69f020000</guid></item><item><title>拉阿纳纳袭击可能预示着来自动荡的约旦河西岸的一波巴勒斯坦恐怖浪潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</link><description>经济危机还可能导致针对巴勒斯坦权力机构的暴力爆发——以色列国防军担心局势可能会恶化——但很难想象内塔尼亚胡会允许西岸工人进入该国 ■ 以色列正在逐步减少在加沙的军事存在，但无法在新的人质释放协议上取得进展</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/raanana-attack-could-herald-a-wave-of-palestinian-terror-from-volatile-west-bank/0000018d-0eeb-de9c-a3df-6ffb1e190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方估计，加沙地带地下隧道网长达 350-450 英里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</link><description>以色列总统将出席达沃斯世界经济论坛，为新的人质协议“增加政治压力” ■ 美国国务卿布林肯表示，“如果加沙再次被夷为平地”，阿拉伯国家将不会重建 ■ 沙特阿拉伯外长表示，如果巴勒斯坦人，沙特将承认以色列问题已解决 ■ 美国袭击也门胡塞武装目标 ■ 在加沙被捕的伊斯兰圣战组织指挥官称该组织成员在伊朗接受训练 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙阵亡的预备役士兵姓名；预备役士兵在加沙战斗中受伤身亡 ■ 以色列南部商店遭火箭弹袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 03:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-live/idf-grave-concern-for-lives-of-two-hostages-iran-claims-to-attack-mossad-hq-in-iraq/0000018d-1055-de9c-a3df-7bfd33c90000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在爱荷华州获胜演讲中表示，如果他是总统，哈马斯就不会攻击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</link><description>前总统击败对手赢得 2024 年首届共和党总统竞选</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/trump-projected-iowa-caucus-winner-staking-early-claim-to-republican-nomination/0000018d-0fe5-db13-affd-7fe5f2bc0000</guid></item><item><title>政府争执推迟向加沙地带哈马斯扣押的以色列人质支付工资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</link><description>10 月 7 日后 100 多天，各部委之间关于如何支付俘虏工资的分歧仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 22:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/government-spats-delay-salary-payments-for-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018d-0eea-db13-affd-7fef55340000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨的 MKs 对他向内塔尼亚胡及其极右翼盟友投降感到沮丧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</link><description>几名政党议员表示，执政联盟中的其他政党曾多次利用其内阁多数席位来违反与民族团结的协议。一位人士表示，“我们总是在自己选择的战斗中失败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 21:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-mks-frustrated-with-his-capitulations-to-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies/0000018d-0ede-de9c-a3df-6fff3ed10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队通知两名哈马斯扣押人质的家人，严重关切他们的生命安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</link><description>“伊泰不是被我们部队射杀的，”以色列国防军发言人在哈马斯播放了伊泰和两名人质的视频一天后的新闻发布会上说。他补充说：“回想起来，我们知道我们袭击的目标就在他们被关押的地点附近。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 20:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/idf-notifies-families-of-two-hamas-held-hostages-of-grave-concern-for-their-lives/0000018d-0e9b-de9c-a3df-6ffb8f0f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>